basics.name: Urian Chang
basics.label: Software Engineer
basics.summary: Software QA engineer looking to transition into a software engineer/developer role. Experienced in web development with modern front-end and back-end technologies, SQL and NoSQL database query languages, and RESTful APIs. Eager to tackle new challenges with a collaborative team and build innovative products.

work.summary: I am currently working as a lead front end developer on a small React team building Insurance applications and I am across multiple applications that have been built or are being built using our new development stack. IAG are keen to utilise the latest front end technologies and we have had great success as a team using React/Redux running on a Node Express server and using an API backend architecture to access the various IAG systems. We are striving to increase the quality of our projects with good test coverage and code reviews and improving our continuous integration practices.
